  ],
  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Your AI agent is bleeding tokens. Right now.",
      "checksum": "sha256:94c39deee7d27f17be1094bb33a09d67d58fe8031d6afe9856d319d22abfefa2",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 2.7399546485260773,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "It just flagged a string of text as a real bug.",
      "checksum": "sha256:13e3631d39668a45adedca30f8654aaa867e6ad72db4d5040962b24dcc29db0b",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 2.5541950113378684,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 8
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "In quotes. Inside a test fixture. Then it billed you to investigate.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6c868fb83eb972ea3e12129eeb8e545cab5f07a76b3740b90c146f43de8febff",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 4.922630385487528,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 19
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Here's the lie. You ask your agent to clean up dee-bug logs.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f9f65c0299cd87c65c0d25648c66890111fbea802736a158219ad42f66683c61",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 31
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "It finds 164 matches across 22 files. But one of them is a test fixture passing the literal string console-dot-log-hi.",
      "checksum": "sha256:bf45af7be7e5d6e06df360ad7ccde1c3e4ceae060ce22d60a36125d54b0c0186",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 7.7090249433106575,
      "word_count": 20,
      "words_offset": 43
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "It's quoted text. Not a real call. Your agent doesn't know.",
      "checksum": "sha256:05eddd615cca5d36244973af690891e266f14862a50f9525944ef540aeceb46e",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 3.622312925170068,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 63
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "One example isn't a pattern. So we tested five common searches.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d9c010a5efc55f9c9c4cfc6a131ae99bfcd91244cd02a0c8790d42f64cdf50bd",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 3.436553287981859,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 74
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Dumb text search over-counted by 26 percent on dee-bug logs.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c5ca18966df815e3c74e73aeb88158465731f971e8b1f0c7c4d64b528498fdcb",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 3.4829931972789114,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 85
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "19 percent on setTimeout. 30 percent on promise chains.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2264074f11776ce0f21c2f7b7ee2bb6226667202b379bb1b4d4ce116c0ad6812",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 95
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "122 percent on useState. Pure billed waste.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8cc6887eb107c6033b249a03acd8df32f8eb7fa0f73bf3de8203ea588d54c8f8",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 2.5541950113378684,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 104
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Translate that into money. 22 files of false positives is roughly 11 thousand tokens.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c6822bb80c6371c36fbda2779d046d7124d236c8141d4fb45f91ce04e08369e7",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 5.433469387755102,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 111
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Call it a cent per refactor. Scale it up.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b716c52016befb7eaabea995ac37cad4567258779403097847578038c2bd5420",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 2.2755555555555556,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 125
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Fifty refactors a day, 30 days a month \u2014 that's 15 dollars per developer.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fef65ac351942f0dd5cee3539a9721a176e78d3eb8a94884b51e49b3083f8282",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 4.504671201814059,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 134
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Just on bad search. Meet ast-grep. It reads your code as code.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f523ead1a9be48288e563a6408ef686e5472bdd3f5ee7fe84b9e19280e3d502c",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 3.7151927437641725,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 148
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "Not as a wall of text. Regular search sees characters. ast-grep sees structure \u2014 functions, calls, try-catch blocks.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cdd31721f453a4664c7f1df7d1a43a2f8b02972ad0a887a34627d8205437cfe8",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 6.919546485260771,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 160
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "The real shape of what you wrote. Three steps.",
      "checksum": "sha256:69e5357e220f84e4bb658629bbf04dcf00279c62eb1088a6e7f8b865a8c8a21b",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 2.461315192743764,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 178
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "One \u2014 tree-sitter parses your code into a tree of nodes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8afcc2f930c007e92bd342129fea490c42e5a57a0cadebdad70d311898200130",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 187
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "Each one tagged by what it actually is. Two \u2014 ast-grep matches patterns against the tree.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ab11eebf9ccc7ed691ba5de6ecd0efc2cc215018bc388fcbfbae5874496132a4",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 5.990748299319728,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 198
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "Not the text. A console-dot-log inside a comment can't match a call pattern.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5b03cf25bcb062836c09b5c18824ed30a54a638d55495c5b42a2cf42b03c2fa1",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 4.365351473922902,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 214
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "Three \u2014 it runs in Rust on every C P U core.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e24f5638acdc06d14ff3ed396405b50c07c10670f94c67919744b12eada9d5da",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 2.693514739229025,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 227
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "Fast. Giving your agent ast-grep takes two commands.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6c8b85fedb76ad1b19acb8990c199d8a52e691f0abf843c025b11272a860e3ae",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 239
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "N P M install dash-G at ast-grep slash C L I.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9784db69239ddddc74c855985468c5e68c5126a0f07bc9d92689ce04f87f1a88",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 3.947392290249433,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 247
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "Then N P X skills add ast-grep slash agent-skill.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7557ed90f824ed07bc302509a3be9b6bdc1b4943997663fd9ab1c387c3f39ffd",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 3.0650340136054424,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 258
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "Restart Claude Code. Tell it: use ast-grep to find.",
      "checksum": "sha256:83846810f23797ae85083097b0f6e5495acfb85c20f3829801ca714078545858",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 3.575873015873016,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 267
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "So here's the question. Your AI agent burns 122 percent more on every refactor than it needs.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7c36370bdd56f7e15f971b058667194f05bdbb24d2d2205a9ec8c5872bed1b32",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 6.222947845804988,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 276
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "One config line. Or accept the waste? Drop your pick in the comments.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1256f82d9245a48e1e6c2c78999739cbcaefd45b1f55838bfad6a832b67a8ff8",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 3.947392290249433,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 293
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "The full breakdown is on this channel. If you want to learn more about AI, check out the dynamous dot AI community.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9f4361825a786943200ac393cd0510bccbb9e46a113446310fe3e32d4fbb7adf",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 6.03718820861678,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 306
    }
  ]
}